 Dashcam footage shows the officers using their patrol vehicles to steer the one ton bison off the road and back to his farm near the city of Round Rock .
As they beep their horns the animal , named Big Boy , continues to run along the sidewalk but he veers in front of the police car and over to the other side of the road .
His owner , Big Boy has got into bad habits recently and has taken to jumping over his fence .